{"tid":1656630,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"葡汁雞翼","createTime":"2019-10-15T16:32:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T01:37:10.000Z","uid":281492,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d27fdfa2759b4b09109d657184d41f2d8aba69ab","tid":1656630,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/16/000903_71a13af2b5c3d0c2840654866dfe0cad.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F16%2F000903_71a13af2b5c3d0c2840654866dfe0cad.jpeg&h=d1732a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自己簡單較個葡汁<br />\n<br />\n味道同出面差唔多 又平<br />\n<br />\n材料：<br />\n<br />\n雞翼一磅 $20<br />\n<br />\n三色椒（每隻色半個）～$5<br />\n<br />\n咖喱磚一小塊 ~$2<br />\n<br />\n椰漿 $8/盒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n步驟：<br />\n<br />\n1. 雞翼解凍後洗乾淨索乾水<br />\n<br />\n2. 用少少鹽同雞粉醃30分鐘（耐啲仲入味）<br />\n<br />\n3. 落鑊中火煎兩面 唔使煎到熟<br />\n<br />\n4. 加熱水（啱啱好蓋過雞翼就得）同咖喱磚<br />\n<br />\n5. 中火煲15分鐘落椰漿<br />\n<br />\n6. 再煲多10分鐘落少少鹽、少少糖、少少豉油<br />\n<br />\n7. 用另一個鑊炒三色椒 落少少鹽嚟炒就得<br />\n<br />\n8. 將炒好嘅三色椒倒落葡汁雞翼度<br />\n<br />\n9. 有黃薑粉可以落埋 顏色會靚啲<br />\n<br />\n10. 細火滾3分鐘落生粉水收汁<br />\n<br />\n11. 可以享用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近除咗眾所周知嘅黃店之外<br />\n<br />\n其他餐廳都唔會貿貿然入去<br />\n<br />\n廢事幫襯錯啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以一得閒都盡量自己煮<br />\n<br />\n減少消費由你我做起<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f97a9ac8b8c123fcd901c50e8aa7bee0acedf0f","tid":1656630,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"49ac9485b893e5583e26a9e554e365860f6b0a45","tid":1656630,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f97a9ac8b8c123fcd901c50e8aa7bee0acedf0f","tid":1656630,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:33:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eD1QUeo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeD1QUeo.jpg&h=564aedde&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:34:44.000Z","msg":"到時見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc95b1d95bc4835b3eb4af6b01278e5a91b5422d","tid":1656630,"uid":221332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽先po 有冇搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37cab04975f83d2f0182e52d23f72abc349cd48b","tid":1656630,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc95b1d95bc4835b3eb4af6b01278e5a91b5422d","tid":1656630,"uid":221332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:36:09.000Z","msg":"夜媽媽先po 有冇搞錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"一個鐘頭前先煮起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n諗住1/4聽日帶飯食 其餘俾老母細妹當晏晝飯"},{"pid":"adb1407cb1c7e6d98892e064364986dd2e3a8b3c","tid":1656630,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想吃"},{"pid":"6a3f466245c3e08be941f6b52d19d63c9bb3b1d7","tid":1656630,"uid":281492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adb1407cb1c7e6d98892e064364986dd2e3a8b3c","tid":1656630,"uid":84102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想吃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"求我吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8016fc98b87a8817d78a2f4529f4dd88983ff138",